WLC_VIEW_SET_CLASS(3)                                    WLC CORE API FUNCTIONS

NAME

    wlc_view_set_class - set class of shell surface

SYNOPSIS

    bool wlc_view_set_class(wlc_handle view, const char *class_);

    Wayland protocol requirements:
        wlc_view_set_class(): shell-surface

DESCRIPTION

    Set class.

RETURN VALUE

    wlc_view_set_class() returns false to indicate failure in attempting to set
    the view class.

